1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,500
Sanibonani.

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:05,500
Ngingumthuthukisi ophakathi kwesiyingi, 연삼흠.

3
00:00:05,500 --> 00:00:08,500
Ngisebenze inkampani iminyaka engu-17,

4
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:14,000
ndisebenzisa i-AI ukuze ngidalwe ama-websites angaphezu kuka-200,
amakhasi angama-600,000.

5
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,000
Le mveliso akuyona entsha.

6
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:20,000
Ithuluzi elikhulile eminyakeni eyi-8 — WIA Geulsalim.

7
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:26,000
I-95% yolwazi lweminyaka engama-5,000 yabantu ayitholakali.

8
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:32,000
I-87% yemibhalo yasenkalakhangeni yaseKorea ayikadijithaliwe
ishonile,

9
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:40,000
ku-97% yezilimi eziyizinkulungwane eziyi-7 emhlabeni,
ikhwalithi yokuhumusha kwe-AI nekhwalithi yokukhuluma iphansi kakhulu noma ayikho.

10
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:45,000
Abantu abangu-300 million abakhubazekile
basilahlekile ukuthintana nezincwadi.

11
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:50,000
Lezi zinsizi ezine kumele zixazululeke ngesikhathi esisodwa.

12
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,500
Geulsalim inepayipi lezi-4 —
ukuvuselela · ukwakha · uguquko · ukudlulisela.

13
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:59,500
Manje sizokunikeza izibonelo ezine
ngokwakho.

14
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:04,000
Isibonelo sokuqala — ukuvuselela.

15
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:10,000
Imodeli ye-Diffusion ivuselela imibhalo yasenkalakhangeni ehlukene,
imodeli yezilimi ifanisa izinhlamvu ezilahlekile.

16
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:14,000
Uhvunyo akuyona ukudlula.

17
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:20,000
I-hash yokuqala igcinwa njalo.

18
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:29,000
Isibonelo sesibili — ukwakha.

19
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:36,000
I-PDF engenatags ye-WCAG 2.2 ihlangatshwa ku-HTML,
i-AI ikwazi ukuhlela ngokuzenzakalelayo nokuqamba umbhalo osemandleni.

20
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:42,000
Kwisayithi yokuhlola ukufinyelela ye-WIA Book,
ngivele ngiyahlola izinto ezingama-80 ngokuzenzakalelayo.

21
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:54,000
Isibonelo sesithathu — ukuvuselela ukufinyelela kwe-EPUB.

22
00:01:54,000 --> 00:02:00,000
I-EPUB 2 engahlangabezani nezidingo izovuselelwa ngokuzenzakalelayo ibe yi-EPUB 3.

23
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:06,000
Iyangena ezifundweni zonke ezingu-80.

24
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:13,000
I-WCAG, i-EPUB A11y, i-KS X 6201, i-European EAA —
ithobela izindinganiso ezine zomhlaba ngasikhathi sinye.

25
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:19,000
Isibonelo sesine — ukudlulisela kokuthile.

26
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:24,000
Iziphumo zesiBhulu ezingu-7,000,
ilimi lokukhuluma elingu-254,

27
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:29,000
I-WIA Talk 3D ye-sign language,
amadivayisi wokukhuluma angama-436 neziqeqebhiso.

28
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:36,000
I-WIA Live, lapho abantu abakhubazekile nendawo eyikhulu bengadingi umhumushi
baxoxa ngqo,

29
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:39,500
sekuqhubeka nezivivinyo.

30
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:43,000
Izincwadi zethu ze-Geulsalim.

31
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:46,000
弘益人間 — ukusiza wonke, kodwa ngaphansi kokugcina.  
We're Geulsalim.
